直方圖

my.plot <- ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat, price, colour = cut))
my.plot <- my.plot + layer(
  geom = "point",
  stat = "identity",
  position = "identity",
  params = list(na.rm = FALSE)
)

my.plot2 <- ggplot(diamonds, aes(x = carat))
my.plot2 <- my.plot2 + layer(
  geom = "bar",
  stat = "bin",
  position = "identity",
  params = list(
    fill = "steelblue",
    binwidth = 0.2,
    na.rm = FALSE
  )
)
my.plot2
